import React from 'react';

const Form = ({submitFn}) => (
    <form onSubmit={submit}>
        <input
            name="name" placeholder="name"
        />
        <input
            name="link" placeholder="link"
        />
        <input
            name="image" placeholder="image"
        />
        <textarea
            name="description"
        />
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
);

export default Form;
